A)3 tier architecture
	-layers:
		a) presentation
		b) business
		c) database
	- Examples:
		a) presentation -> ASP.NET
		b) business -> c#
		c) database -> SQL
	
B)Monoliths
	- single-tiered
	- components:
		a) presentation
		b) business logic
		c) Database layer
	- features:
		a) Simple to develop
		b) deployement is easy
	- drawbacks:
		a) Maintenance
		b) updation is difficult
		
C) Microservices
	- loosely coupled services
	- connected via API gateway
	- features:
		a) Faster application
		b) good for large application
	- drawbacks:
		a) complex structure
		b) testing is difficult
